OL,3,CMeet the man walking 100 miles in just
OL,4,Ca pair of socks
OL,6,FWalking in Cumbria is a popular
OL,7,Factivity, and so are hikes along
OL,8,FHadrian's Wall, but for one 25-year-
OL,9,Fold he is taking things a step further.
OL,11,FKai Flynn, from Manchester, is walking
OL,12,F100 miles just in his socks with no
OL,13,Fwalking boots, no trainers and not
OL,14,Feven sandals. He'll be tackling the
OL,15,Fjourney from Silloth to Druridge Bay
OL,16,Fin Northumberland.
OL,18,FHe expects the challenge will take
OL,19,Faround 20 days and he's doing it to
OL,20,Fhelp raise awareness for men's mental
OL,21,Fhealth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
