OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1774271469
OL,3,CMeet the man walking 100 miles in just
OL,4,Ca pair of socks
OL,6,FKai said: "The pain that I'm going
OL,7,Fthrough currently is nothing compared
OL,8,Fto the pain of other people that
OL,9,Fthey're struggling alone at the moment.
OL,11,F"It starts conversations, to start
OL,12,Faddressing these mental health
OL,13,Fstigmas." He hopes the socks will get
OL,14,Fpeople talking as he walks along the
OL,15,Froute."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
