CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F359A1774271469
OL,3,CMeet the man walking 100 miles in just
OL,4,Ca pair of socks
OL,6,FHe's raising money for two charities
OL,7,Fwhich means a lot to him and have
OL,8,Fhelped him during his life, he says
OL,9,Fthat Breaking Barriers got him "out of
OL,10,Fa very bad situation" and that Andy's
OL,11,FMan Club led him to "start opening up
OL,12,Fon realising that I wasn't alone."
OL,14,F"I didn't have the best start to life.
OL,15,FI struggled for quite a long time,"
OL,16,FKai explains.
OL,18,F"Just to be able to give back is
OL,19,Fgenuinely what keeps me going in life."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
