OL,3,CMeet the man walking 100 miles in just
OL,4,Ca pair of socks
OL,6,FHe runs a social media account
OL,7,Fhighlighting his adventures, in fact
OL,8,Fthis shoeless walk is a cooldown
OL,9,Fcompared to the challenge he did last
OL,10,Fsummer, walking from Manchester to
OL,11,FMilan
OL,13,FThe 25-year-old is already a week into
OL,14,Fthe challenge, he says they're
OL,15,F"covered in blisters."
OL,17,F"It's very painful for the first half
OL,18,Fan hour. An hour getting into the
OL,19,Fwalk, it's manageable.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
